skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: should i exercise
des:
We get it. Sometimes it's hard to exercise. Sometimes you need a buddy to give you that extra push. So let Alexa give you that bit of extra motivation to push yourself, exercise and get that summer beach body.

Once you enable the skill, simply say "Alexa, should I exercise?" to let Alexa push you to exercise. She'll ask if you're ready to exercise. If you still aren't, feel free to say "No" to hear more motivation.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
